类 ScanModifyingObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.example.ScanModifyingObserver
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Coprocessor, RegionCoprocessor, RegionObserver

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ScanModifyingObserver
extends Object
implements RegionCoprocessor, RegionObserver
    A RegionObserver which modifies incoming Scan requests to include additional columns than what the user actually requested.
